ðŸ“„ Data Security Policy for Entro8

At Entro8, we take your data security seriously.
Protection Measures:
* All communications are encrypted (SSL/TLS).
* Sensitive data is securely stored (Firebase Authentication, Firestore encryption).
* No plain-text storage of passwords or critical user information.
* Regular security audits and compliance checks.
User Rights:
* Users can request their data or account be deleted at any time.
* Minimal data retention is practiced unless legally required for compliance.
Compliance:
* Our data handling practices are aligned with GDPR, CCPA, and other applicable privacy regulations.

